The following is a list of acronyms used in the titles of many of the 34 data parts in this collection: AN1 -- 1st Annual Post-Test; AN2 -- 2nd Annual Post-Test; AVLT -- Rey Auditory Verbal Learning Test; BL AVLT -- Baseline Rey Auditory Verbal Learning Test; CRT -- Complex Reaction Time; EPT -- Everyday Problems Test; HVLT -- Hopkins Verbal Learning Test; OTDL -- Observed Tasks of Daily Living; PAN1 -- 1st Annual Post-Test; PT -- Post-Test; PT AVLT -- Post-Test Baseline Rey Auditory Verbal Learning Test; Rivermead -- Rivermead Behavioral Memory Test; UFOV -- Useful Field of Vision;  
 The Rey AVLT used in this data collection is a subset of the full Rey test. 
 Only a particular subset of the Rivermead Behavioral Memory Test was used for ACTIVE.

